Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:30.17,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:36.77,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.18,0:00:44.18,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.26,0:00:51.46,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:01:00.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:05.71,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.78,0:01:10.65,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.72,0:01:15.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.39,0:01:23.23,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,时值公元1890年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.87,0:01:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,经历重重冒险之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.47,0:01:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好不容易终于抵达非洲大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喜欢上在当地认识的男孩 却尝到失恋滋味的娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.68,0:01:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失去了再次振作的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就剩下没几话了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:48.75,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,34 心爱的娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,1 2 3 4 5 6 7 8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他对她轻声说道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,『今晚看不到什么星星』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到了非洲之后 也发生了好多事情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:22.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 玛莉也长大了很多喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没想到会在这种地方 遇到那个名字是『冈』开头的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝也遇到了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.60,0:02:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.97,0:02:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是长颈鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.57,0:02:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长颈鹿？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.31,0:02:40.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 在那边的是河马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起来好呆喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后在那里的则是非洲象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,简直像是动物园一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那不是狮子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.62,0:02:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狮子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是跟大王长得不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.93,0:03:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王还只是个小宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长大之后就会变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好怪喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.54,0:03:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好蠢喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真羡慕玛莉 总是很有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.49,0:03:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.86,0:03:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为那个来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呆瓜 是失恋啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.06,0:03:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 人生最大的逆境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚她不会有事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你真是个好人\N强 你真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 你也真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你喜欢上的可是那个娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该早就做好心理准备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我没料到会是这么辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听好 强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你晓得爱上女人 是怎么一回事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.63,0:04:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是地狱\N就是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地狱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错\N没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古今中外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再没有比交女朋友 更麻烦辛苦的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是14 15岁 初恋的女孩那还好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是沉醉在爱情中 就能让他们感到满意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 年龄再大点的可就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 一下要礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.53,0:04:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要约会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要你带她去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.06,0:04:42.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要你陪她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要你不要搞错她的年纪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要你不准看其他女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要你请她吃美食
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要你讲笑话逗她笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下要你接送
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,烦都烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱上对方的男人 注定得对她有求必应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唯有能忍受那种地狱折磨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸福才会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 是啊 这种苦头我以前也尝过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.69,0:05:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错\N没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然关键还是在于契机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听好 强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱情是要彼此都意识到 才有办法开花结果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚是有那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你只是还没找到契机罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.61,0:05:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我该怎么做才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个要你自己想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本来是想这么跟你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回就特别优待给你建议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唱情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,情歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没有不被情歌打动的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.26,0:05:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听好 强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是个千载难逢的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,投入你所有的科学技术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倾注你所有的爱意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,写出一首情歌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.04,0:06:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向娜蒂亚传达你的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对 好比说这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ah~你正爱着某个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ah~有如烈火般的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.38,0:06:44.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ah~抛开泪水踏上旅程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.35,0:06:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和我们一起去寻找真爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心爱的人不就在你面前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人是无法独自活下去的 (我是认真的)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你必须体会何谓真爱 (这是命令)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人生中的邂逅都是注定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在 最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.92,0:07:27.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是梦想 就是恋爱 就是爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,(真是残酷啊)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然还是得靠情歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:22.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的名字是强·洛克·拉帝格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:29.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是正义与爱的科学家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,敏锐的直觉 丰富的想像力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.23,0:08:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的理论完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 这片大海
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧 那片宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开朗的明日将创造未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:01.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,GO GO GO GO Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,GO GO GO GO FlGHT GO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱情就要觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…
